102
00:10:49,229 --> 00:10:51,930
Beri tahu aku jika ada yang bisa kubantu.

103
00:10:53,800 --> 00:10:56,200
Aku berencana menyingkirkan antek Jepang itu.

104
00:10:56,269 --> 00:10:57,800
"Antek, informan"

105
00:10:58,499 --> 00:10:59,700
Count Noda.

106
00:11:01,340 --> 00:11:02,570
Song Byeong Su.

107
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:22,190
Kepala Ahli Bedah Ishida sedang di ruang bedah.

108
